title: Remodeled and upgraded 3 bedroom 2 bath
posting_body: ['VIDEO TOUR', 'Please click on the link below to see a video tour of the property:', '<URL>', 'SHOWING SCHEDULE', 'After you review the video, please let us know the best time and date for you to view the property.', 'PROPERTY FEATURES', '- $5100 monthly rent', '- $5100 security deposit', '- 1 year lease minimum', '- 2 car side by side garage parking', '- 3 bedroom 2 bathrooms', '- 1900 approx sq ft (un-verified)', '- Remodeled and upgraded to modern tastes', '- Separate water, gas and electric meters', '- Tenant to pay all utilities', '- Close to highly desired school district', '- Close proximity to El Camino Real and all of the shops and restaurants that come with that.', '- Close to Millbrae CalTrain, BART and other transportation options', '- Close to parks and recreational areas', '- Small town feel with big city amenities', '- Laundry room (Washer and dryer tenant to provide or tenant may lease from property manager)', '- Equal opportunity housing for all.', 'APPLICATION PROCESS', 'We will need the email addresses of all the adult applicants in order to process the online application.', "An email will be sent to you from TransUnion's <URL> platform which will charge each adult applicant $40.", "This charge will cover each adult applicant's credit history, criminal background check and eviction history report.", 'We do not accept any reports from other sources.', 'Also, please email us:', '1.', 'Your projected move in date', '2.', "A copy of all adult occupants driver's license", '3.', 'Copy of past 2 pay stubs', '4.', "Employer's contact information", '5.', 'Previous landlord contact information.', '6.', 'Your position at work/job title', '7.', 'The nature of your work', '8.', 'We may need additional documentation based on your initial application package.', 'Please note the application processing will take a minimum of 48 to 72 business hours.', "New Generation Investments and it's clients/landlords provide equal housing opportunity."]
